name: these 7000 oaks do not exist
description: This work is a cross between Joseph Beuys' "7000 Oaks" and "This Cat Does Not Exist", which questions the environmental impact of NFT's and celebrates the 100th anniversary of Joseph Beuys. This NFT consists of a number of 7000 images of oak trees generated from over 10,000 using the platform.io machine learning system.
